{"tid":2194191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"通訊軟件頭像寫抗爭口號遭停學一週 香島警告學生再參與即踢出校","createTime":"2020-09-08T11:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:38:38.000Z","uid":303304,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c1368cba9fba4dd0cd67e2966e779abd7d43cb","tid":2194191,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"直資左校香島中學再爆打壓學生事件，一名中四學生因在網上溝通軟件的個人介紹上寫上抗爭口號，遭校方處分，不僅要求該同學立即停學一星期，更警告不可再參與任何社會運動，否則立即開除學籍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/PC4SKIXJEFC2VGF7XBMCNOI5BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FPC4SKIXJEFC2VGF7XBMCNOI5BA%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=deaae1bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FPC4SKIXJEFC2VGF7XBMCNOI5BA%2F&h=f9b54dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/PC4SKIXJEFC2VGF7XBMCNOI5BA/</a><br />\n<br />\nfrom apple daily"},{"pid":"6fae5e2cb3c694b399b26a3aeed6b021ab315794","tid":2194191,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:02:56.000Z","msg":"據關注組引述該名學生指，當時校方也有邀請學生的家長出席會面，而校長在會面上更提到會嚴肅跟進事件。校長形容事件已經傷害學校，指學生經常藉機會與學校對着幹，小事化大，令校方需要對外解釋，又揚言希望涉事學生能「轉換環境」，指對學生並沒信心，更稱開除學籍是對學生最好選擇，「佢（學生）隨時又搞單嘢，到時我同佢就攬住死㗎喇」。"},{"pid":"8a022637bc6a0e6695c2855229ff8a25e1cd9d56","tid":2194191,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"香島中學早前亦被爆出政治審查風波，一名任教逾12年的姓李藝術科教師向師生發公開信，指校董會不滿她未阻止學生音樂考試時演奏《願榮光歸香港》，疑因此不予續約，事件揭發後逾百名學生於校外拉起人鏈聲援老師，警方更一度到場。"},{"pid":"96439bd41988f2dc12e4538482eaae0b509461a3","tid":2194191,"uid":303304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"要睇全文請自己訂閣蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6212df9ebb1e658b69a97c3c70dd1e8e67a107b3","tid":2194191,"uid":313054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8faca5b3500f32671c557a600e5b9a4eed28bc8","tid":2194191,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cf0fc401a9549b34fa1b31560de8bb0ddae3bc","tid":2194191,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"紅校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9020f6d3296e87f68266999d6f8cf74254ca53e","tid":2194191,"uid":229880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"香島咁愛國點解要用Microsoft teams??"},{"pid":"5e776d8657776afc647db4f8aa5839b35df28fb1","tid":2194191,"uid":63843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"點解個名咁似中文考試既虛構學校名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2291deecb2af21b51fdd397fdda1d6ba914fef","tid":2194191,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"踢咪踢囉 , 當自己哈佛咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787bbf2b0612df722b4a9bd311cc981167b9b3d3","tid":2194191,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<